   <text:p text:style-name="P25"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P25">Ne scap din nevoi. Curagiu | N-avei team, cci sint n agonie Fiastrii rei noastre... i moartea nu-ntirzie.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P25"/>
